267
00:16:59,530 --> 00:17:01,760
Aku dilarang meninggalkan Korea.

268
00:17:02,630 --> 00:17:04,659
Tae Suk juga yang bertanggung jawab atas Joon

269
00:17:06,069 --> 00:17:07,430
